          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A beam of monoenergetic electrons from a 25-MeV",
                "betatron passed through a tin foil, thereby producing",
                "bremsstrahlung gamma rays. These bremsstrahlung",
                "produced gamma rays were scattered from a natural",
                "strontium target and detected by a NaI detector",
                "placed at 131 degrees with respect to the direction",
                "of the incident gamma rays. High isotopic abundance",
                "of 88Sr implies that there is practically no",
                "contribution to the scattering process from 87Sr.",
                "86Sr may account for about one eighth of the",
                "scattered gamma rays."
              ]
            }
          ],
